data.description: Welcome to an exquisite property located in one of the most sought-after age restricted 55 + communities! This stunning single-story home offers a private courtyard and plenty of upgrades for comfortable living. The attached next gen suite with kitchenette is the perfect place to make any guest feel at home. Amazing views of the Frenchmen Mountains greet you as you enter into the home. A chef’s kitchen equipped GE stainless steel appliances and a large island with quartz countertops create a modern and refined atmosphere. Additional features in this home are luxury vinyl plank flooring, upgraded carpet in select rooms, and a Kinetico water softener system. Step outside and relax in the private courtyard, or head to the nearby clubhouse and enjoy the wonderful amenities the community has to offer. Completed in May 2023 with a builder warranty until  May 2024. Don’t miss this incredible opportunity!
